STDHT_MGN12_NOVA		 MAKE 8
PTFE_Guide Comes with BMG clones MAKE 1 Make from 4mm OD PTFE tube:
1 - Using Xacto blade, create internal chamfer in one end.
2 - Cut that end into an arrow shape (try to match the angle from the HextrudORT body where the hobb gears meet.
3 - Insert into HextrudORT body and cut excess length flush.

STDHT_MGN12_NOVA		 BUY 9
NOVA HotEnd From 3DPassion.com BUY 1 BE AWARE, if using the 100W heater cartridge available for NOVA, Duet might trigger errors during PID tune due to too much overshoot (default 15C).
This can be resolved by Inserting an M570 H1* T25 in your config file.
* is your heater number.
Klipper seems to be handling this power without any issue.
